premise_source_doc_sentence: Its release was limited and it ultimately grossed US$ 8 million on a budget of US$ 18 million .
The storm was deemed the worst ice storm in a decade for New England and the most severe ice storm in 21 years for Upstate New York .
The December 2008 Northeastern United States ice storm was a damaging ice storm that took out power for millions of people in those regions .
A total of 24 people were killed , and as many as 1.8 million people were left without electricity on December 6 .
The Ice Storm is a 1997 American drama film directed by Ang Lee , based on the 1994 novel of the same name by Rick Moody .
